text: Kyra may refer to: ==Places== * Kyra, Cyprus, a village in Cyprus * Kyra, Russia, a rural locality (a selo) in Zabaykalsky Krai, Russia * Kyra River, a river in Kyra, Russia ==Other== * Kyra (Charmed), fictional character from the TV series Charmed * KYRA (FM), a radio station (92.7 FM) licensed to serve Thousand Oaks, California, United States * Kyra (given name) * Kyra, a former snout moth genus of the Phycitini, now synonymized with Eurhodope ==See also== * Kira (disambiguation)
title: Kyra
